Video-Xine version 0.04
=======================

This is an interface to the xine-lib library. It can be used to create
a Perl-controlled instance of Xine.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  xine-lib, available from http://xinehq.de

In addition, if you wish to actually display video, you probably want:

  X11::FullScreen

which provides a workable, if extremely simple, user interface.

